# Creating a Microsoft Azure Pass Subscription

Creating an Azure Pass subscription is a two step process.

1. Redeem your Azure Pass Promo Code  
1. Activate your subscription

## Step 1: Redeeming a Microsoft Azure Pass Promo Code:

- [] Open a browser and navigate to: @[www.microsoftazurepass.com][azure-pass]{powershell}

    > [!KNOWLEDGE] It is recommended you close all browsers and open a new In-Private Browser session. Other log-ins can persist and cause errors during the activation step.

- [] Click the start button to get started.
	
    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/1.jpg)	

- [] Enter your account login information and select “Sign In”.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/2.jpg)
	
- []Click “Confirm” if the correct email address is listed.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/3.jpg)
	
- [] Enter your promo code (available from the **Resources** tab above) in the Promo code box and click “Claim Promo Code”.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/4.jpg)
	
- [] It may take up to 5 minutes to process the redemption.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/5.jpg)

- [] Click on “Activate” to start setting up your Azure subscription.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/6.jpg)
	
## Step 2: Activate your subscription:

- []Enter your account information and click “Next”.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/7.jpg)
	
- [] Enter your phone number and click “Next”.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/8.jpg)
	
- [] It may take a few minutes to process the request.

    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/9.jpg)
    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/10.jpg)
    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/11.jpg)
	
- []Your subscription is ready, click “Get started” to use Azure services.
	
    !IMAGE[](https://lodmanuals.blob.core.windows.net/manuals/LODS%20Media/Azure%20Pass%20How-To/12.jpg)

[azure-pass]:
```
Start-Process 'www.microsoftazurepass.com'
```
